pan>.<span class=\"name\">val</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Std/Sat/AIG/Basic.html#Std.Sat.AIG.Fanin\">Fanin</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Std/Sat/AIG/Basic.lean#L34-L34","name":"Std.Sat.AIG.Fanin.ofRaw","line":34,"kind":"ctor","docLink":"./Std/Sat/AIG/Basic.html#Std.Sat.AIG.Fanin.ofRaw","doc":""},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Sat/AIG/Basic.html#Std.Sat.AIG.Fanin.ofRaw\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sat</span>.<span class=\"name\">AIG</span>.<span class=\"name\">Fanin</span>.<span class=\"name\">ofRaw</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">val</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Std/Sat/AIG/Basic.html#Std.Sat.AIG.Fanin\">Fanin</a></div></div>"},{"info":{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/ad1a017949674a947f0d6794cbf7130d642c6530/src/Std/Sat/AIG/Basic.lean#L27-L36","name":"Std.Sat.AIG.Fanin","line":27,"kind":"structure","docLink":"./Std/Sat/AIG/Basic.html#Std.Sat.AIG.Fanin","doc":"This datatype is isomorphic to a pair of a `Nat` and a `Bool`, however the `Bool` is stored in the\nlowest bit of the `Nat` in order to save memory. It is used to describe an input to an `AIG` circuit\nnode which consists of a `Nat` describing the input node and a `Bool` saying whether there is an inverter\non the input.\n"},"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Sat/AIG/Basic.html#Std.Sat.AIG.Fanin\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Sat</span>.<span class=\"name\">AIG</span>.<span class=\"name\">Fanin</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>"}]}